A simple platform game created as part of the course TDDC76. LiTH HT2012.

Required to compile:
SDL
SDL_mixer
SDL_ttf
SDL_image
OpenGL Mathematics (GLM) 

Controlls:
SPACE - Jump
A - Move left
D - Move right
R - Reload
M - Mute background music
Left mouse button - Fire
Mouse - Aim
Mouse scroll - Change weapons

Install: Compile and run feed. Make sure you have a data/saves folder. 

